		<div class="edge-mockup">
			<%= image_tag 'ThinManager-Core-Server.png' %> 
		</div>
		<div class="row edge-heading">
			<h1>The Core <span class="goAwaySooner"><br /></span>of Device Configuration and Deployment</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-lg-12">
				<p>The all new Core from ThinManager provides a turnkey solution for configuring and deploying the world's most advanced thin client management system. Core comes preloaded with Windows Server 2016, TS Cals, pre-activated RDS licenses and, of course, ThinManager.</p>

				<p>The Core Server device incorporates new ThinManager plug-n-play technology which auto-senses ThinManager-Ready devices and pre-configures them for immediate deployment. Core  also auto-senses other Edge devices so that redundancy is automatically enabled when connected additional Edge devices to your network.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<br /><span class="goAway"><br /></span>
		<div class="row sub-points">
			<div class="col-md-3">
				<h3>Core Cloud Services</h3>
				<p>Edge devices can be easily configured to connect to ThinManager Core Cloud Services. ThinManager CCS can store configurations and other important data in the secure cloud. ACP provides several APIs for connecting your ThinManager plant floor data to ERP or other enterprise software platforms used to analyze and share information at the corporate level.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-3 col-md-offset-1">
				<h3>Your Core Plant Floor</h3>
				<p>ThinManager customers have always used the platform as the go-to solution for managing every PC, thin client and mobile device. Now, that same solution brings all of the ease-of-use of ThinManager to the server.</p>

				<p>The Core server supports ThinManager's powerful new virtualization technology (DRIVE) Deployable Resource in Virtualized Environment. Using the Core configuration wizard, administrator's can easily virtualize their Remote Desktop Server(s) without incurring any additional costs for a third part virtualization solution.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-3 col-md-offset-1">
				<h3>The Core of the Future</h3>
				<p>Centralized, client-based deployment is now widely accepted as the best way to deploy and manage plant floor applications and devices. The new ThinManager Core now makes using thin technology as easy as opening the box, plugging it in and turning it on. Don't waste your time and money piecing together a thin client solution. Gaining the edge on your competition begins at the Core.</p>
			</div>
